text: Guido Andreozzi and Ariel Behar were the defending champions but only Behar chose to defend his title, partnering Thiago Monteiro. Behar lost in the first round to David Pérez Sanz and Oriol Roca Batalla. Kevin Krawietz and Andreas Mies won the title after defeating Sander Gillé and Joran Vliegen 7–6(8–6), 2–6, [10–6] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Casino Admiral Trophy - Doubles
title: 2019 Casino Admiral Trophy – Doubles
